Author: Bryan Jimenez

myserver is a tiny multiprocessed server that will serve html pages with images, css, and javascript.

to compile:

unzip under the unpbook-code folder
make and run myserver

to use:

point your browser to the ip(127.0.0.1 if in the same machine) and port(55555 by default, can be changed in the source) of myserver
myserver will serve pages in the "www" folder by default (can be changed in the source)






